#MEM id=rules source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/mia/skills/design-and-build/vercel-react-best-practices/rules/bundle-barrel-imports.md savings=3%
M||tx|---
M||titl|Avoid Barrel File Imports
M||impa|ct
M||impa|200-800ms import cost, slow builds
M||tags|bundle, imports, tree-shaking, barrel-files, perf
M||tx|---
M|Avoi|tx|Import directly from source files instead of barrel files to avoid loading thousands of unused modules. **Barrel files** are entry points that re-export multiple modules (e.g., `index.js` that does `export * from './md'`).
M|Avoi|tx|Popular icon and cp libraries can have **up to 10,000 re-exports** in their entry file. For many rc packages, **it takes 200-800ms just to import them**, affecting both dv speed and production cold starts.
M|Avoi|**Wh|** When a library is marked as external (not bundled), the bundler can't op it. If you bundle it to enable tree-shaking, builds become substantially slower analyzing the entire md graph.
M|Avoi|**In|**
M|Avoi|tx|```tsx
M|Avoi|tx|import { Check, X, Menu } from 'lucide-rc'
M|Avoi|tx|// Loads 1,583 modules, takes ~2.8s extra in dv
M|Avoi|// R|200-800ms on every cold start
M|Avoi|tx|import { Button, TextField } from '@mui/material'
M|Avoi|tx|// Loads 2,225 modules, takes ~4.2s extra in dv
M|Avoi|tx|```
M|Avoi|**Co|**
M|Avoi|tx|```js
M|Avoi|tx|// nx.config.js - automatically optimizes barrel imports at bd time
M|Avoi|tx|md.exports = {
M|Avoi|expe|{
M|Avoi|opti|['lucide-rc', '@mui/material']
M|Avoi|tx|}
M|Avoi|tx|}
M|Avoi|tx|```
M|Avoi|tx|```tsx
M|Avoi|tx|// Keep the standard imports - nx.js transforms them to direct imports
M|Avoi|tx|import { Check, X, Menu } from 'lucide-rc'
M|Avoi|tx|// Full ts support, no manual path wrangling
M|Avoi|tx|```
M|Avoi|tx|This is the recommended approach bc it preserves ts tp safety and editor autocompletion while still eliminating the barrel import cost.
M|Avoi|**Co|**
M|Avoi|tx|```tsx
M|Avoi|tx|import Button from '@mui/material/Button'
M|Avoi|tx|import TextField from '@mui/material/TextField'
M|Avoi|tx|// Loads only what you use
M|Avoi|tx|```
M|Avoi|> **|** Some libraries (notably `lucide-rc`) don't ship `.d.ts` files for their deep import paths. Importing from `lucide-rc/dist/esm/icons/check` resolves to an implicit `any` tp, causing er under `strict` or `noImplicitAny`. Prefer `optimizePackageImports` when available, or verify the library exports tp for its subpaths before using direct imports.
M|Avoi|tx|These optimizations provide 15-70% faster dv boot, 28% faster builds, 40% faster cold starts, and significantly faster HMR.
M|Avoi|Libr|`lucide-rc`, `@mui/material`, `@mui/icons-material`, `@tabler/icons-rc`, `rc-icons`, `@headlessui/rc`, `@radix-ui/rc-*`, `lodash`, `ramda`, `date-fns`, `rxjs`, `rc-use`.
M|Avoi|Refe|[How we optimized pk imports in nx.js](https://vc.com/blog/how-we-optimized-pk-imports-in-nx-js)